snippet.title: BFDI: Branches - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
I’ve been waiting to show all of you guys this new project I’ve been working on!

BFDI: Branches is an all-new platformer game with Firey, Leafy, Coiny, and Pin! Featuring multiple characters with varied gameplay, a story mode with branching paths, a complete level editor, and an online level browser!

More info here:
https://teambranches.itch.io/bfdi-branches

https://discord.gg/bfdibranches

See you guys soon!
